TIMetaTemplate.displayName.RW7_Scenario=Pax Bharata
TIMetaTemplate.description.RW7_Scenario=An alternate Earth: the Mongol khanates never fully receded, Indian merchant powers rule the oceans from Zanzibar to Honolulu, a sprawling nuclear caliphate ages in Baghdad, and Europe is a fractured periphery. After centuries of subcontinental peace, Punjabi tanks roll towards New Delhi, a fact the world would call the shock of the century if an alien craft had not just fallen out of the sky.<br/><h>Pax Bharata</h>
